English: Secure one-stop digital asset financial service platform
Chinese: 安全一站式数字资产金融服务平台

English: Digital assets, mastered at one hand; multi-currency cross-chain, one-stop management
Chinese: 数字资产，一手掌握；多币种跨链，一站式管理

English: Scan code download to open a new financial journey
Chinese: 扫码下载，开启全新的金融之旅

English: PI redefines the concept of stable currency, which is a stable currency with asset mortgage protection, decentralization, anti-fluctuation, and interest rate increase. Any user with PI can exercise the same monetary rights in the digital financial world as in traditional economic society.
Chinese: PI 对稳定币概念进行重新定义，是一种具有资产抵押保障、去中心、抗波动、可增息的稳定币。任何持有PI的用户皆可在数字金融世界行使与传统经济社会中一样的货币权利

English: Multi-currency cross-chain transfer, multi-purpose use of chain assets
Chinese: 多币种跨链转入，链资产多元用途

English: You can only get PI related services on the Chrome desktop browser
Chinese: 您只能在Chrome桌面浏览器上获取PI相关服务

English: You have not installed PI officially specified browser wallet Asilink, please download and install and log in and try again
Chinese: 您暂未安装PI官方指定浏览器钱包Asilink，请下载安装并登陆后再次尝试

English: Go to the Google Store to download
Can't open Google Store? Click to download the installation package directly
Chinese: 打不开谷歌商店? 点击直接下载安装包

English: PI asset total value equals PI wallet balance plus deposit balance
Chinese: PI资产总值等于PI钱包余额加上存款余额

English: Stable currency based on asset pledge
Chinese: 基于资产质押发行的稳定币

English: Depending on the currency characteristics, market conditions, and the term of the loan, Pipay will have multiple different borrowing
Chinese: 根据币种特性，行情，以及借款期限，Pipay借PI会有多个不同的借款利率，您可按需选择

English: Please enter a amount of no less than{{value}}{{value}}.
The number of inputs is greater than the available balance
Chinese: 输入数量大于可用余额

English: Start calculation after confirmation of the transaction
Chinese: 于交易确认后开始计算

English: I have read and agree to Pipay to deposit PI income rules and risk tips.
Chinese: 我已阅读并同意Pipay存PI收息规则及风险提示

English: Do not leave the current page
Waiting for the validator to package the transaction into blocks
Chinese: 等待验证者把交易打包入块

English: Sorry, the transaction was not received by the blockchain. Please check the transaction format and re-initiate the transaction.
Chinese: 对不起，交易没有被区块链接收，请仔细检查交易格式并重新发起交易

English: The transaction has not yet been packaged, you can check the status of the transaction in the "Deposit History" and the transaction may be successful at any time.
Chinese: 交易尚未被打包，您可以在“存款记录”中查看交易状态，交易可能随时成功。

English: Once the transaction is successful, we will update your trading results immediately.
Chinese: 交易成功后，我们会立即更新您的交易结果。

English: Your {{value}}day time deposit {{value}} has been successfully saved
Chinese: 您的{{value}}天定期存款{{value}}已成功存入

English: {{value}} days of time deposit, {{value}} days remaining
Please enter the number of PI you want to remove
Chinese: 请输入您想要取出的PI的数量

English: The deposit has expired and has been automatically converted to demand deposit
Chinese: 存款已到期，已自动转为活期存款

English: *The number of inputs is greater than the available balance
The currency you choose to pledge your loan and the amount you need to pledge
Chinese: 您选择的用于质押借款的币种和需要质押的金额

English: The pledge rate is the ratio of the value of the pledged assets to the value of the borrowed assets. The higher the pledge rate, the more reliable the loan order. Since each of Pipay's borrowings is based on a single currency, each currency has its own global value.
Chinese: 质押率是指质押资产与借出资产的价值之比，质押率越高，借贷订单越可靠，由于Pipay的每次借款都是基于单个币种借出，因此每个币种会有自己的全局质押率

English: The real-time market price of the asset used for pledge, used to calculate the pledge rate
Chinese: 用于质押的资产的实时市场价格，会用于计算质押率

English: When the pledged assets fall to the liquidation price, in order to avoid risks, the system will automatically liquidate the borrowings for settlement of loans and fines.
Chinese: 当质押资产跌至清算价格时，为避免风险，系统将自动清算本借款单，用于结算借款和罚金

English: When the liquidation occurs, the proportion of funds used to compensate the system is deducted from the pledged assets.
Chinese: 在清算发生时，从质押资产中扣除用于补偿系统的资金比例

English: Your {{value}} asset balance is not sufficient to pledge,still need {{value}}
Chinese: 您的{{value}}资产余额不满足所需数量，还差{{value}}

English: At least the pledge is insufficient to recharge
Chinese: 质押物不足至少还需充值

English: Your {{value}} loan {{value}} has been successfully paid, please check it in time
Chinese: 您的{{value}}借款{{value}}已出款成功，请及时查看

English: With {{value}} days loaned with the due on demand order
Increasing the pledge assets can increase the pledge rate and ensure the stability of the order. Please enter the amount of the pledged assets you want to deposit.
Chinese: 增加质押资产能提高质押率，保证订单的稳定，请输入您要存入的质押资产数额

English: Whether to cancel this loan order
Chinese: 是否取消本次借款订单

English: The price of the pledge {{value}} is approaching the liquidation price, please add the {{value}} pledge in time, or repay the loan in advance.
Chinese: 质押的{{value}}价格下跌逼近清算价格，请及时追加{{value}}质押，或提前还款

English: Due to the falling price of the pledge, this order has been cleared for liquidation
Chinese: 由于质押物价格下跌，本订单已进行爆仓清算

English: The liquidation of the pledge assets is used to repay the debts and pay the fines. If there is any remaining pledge, the original will be returned.
Chinese: 清算会拍卖质押资产用于偿还债务和付罚金，清算完成若有剩余质押物，会原路退回

English: The loan has been paid off, the pledged assets have been returned, and the order has been closed.
Chinese: 借款已还清，质押资产已退回，订单已关闭

English: Regular {{value}} address can receive {{value}} transfers from non-Asimov chains
Chinese: 常规{{value}}地址可以接收来自非Asimov链的{{value}}转账

English: 1. The {{value}} cross-chain receive address will be updated from time to time. Please do not save the address or QR code in other places.
Chinese: 1. {{value}}跨链收款地址会不定时更新，请不要在其它地方保存地址或二维码图片重复使用

English: 2. Before each payment, please go to this interface to get the latest payment address.
Chinese: 2. 每次收款之前，请到本界面获取最新的收款地址

English: 3. Cross-chain receive requires a longer waiting time than a normal transaction. You can follow the transaction progress in the transaction details interface.
Chinese: 3. 跨链收款需要相对普通交易较长的等待时间，您可在交易详情界面关注交易进度

English: 4. If you accidentally put {{value}} into the old address, please contact customer service in time.
Chinese: 4. 如果不小心将{{value}}打入到旧地址，请及时联系客服处理

English: Enter address or select recent payee
Chinese: 输入地址或选择最近收款人

English: Enter the number of {{value}} you want to transfer
The deposit has been withdrawn in advance and the order is closed
Chinese: 存款已提前取出，订单结束

English: You can automatically enjoy the benefits
As long as there is a PI in your wallet balance, you can get the earning every day, issue it regularly, and automatically arrive at the account.
Chinese: 只要您的钱包余额里面有PI，就可以每天获得收益，定时发放，自动到账

English: Scan code to transfer PI to yourself
Q. How much does it need to be deposited to earn interest?
Chinese: Q. 需要存入多少才能获得利息？

English: A. According to the current price of PI, the current interest rate of the system, your wallet balance needs to have at least 100 PI to get interest.
Chinese: A. 根据PI当前的价格已经系统当前的利率，您的钱包余额需要有至少100 PI 才能获得利息

English: Q. How do I get interest?
A. The system will automatically calculate the interest you can get based on your real-time balance, and automatically transfer the interest to your wallet balance.
Chinese: A. 系统会根据您的实时余额，自动计算您可获得的利息，自动将利息定时转入您的钱包余额

English: Q. What if I don't have a PI? / Where can I get more PI?
Chinese: Q. 没有PI怎么办？/哪里可以获得更多PI？

English: A. PI is a stable currency. All PIs are issued through pledge lending. You can lend a certain PI by pledge, or you can go to the trading market to buy PI.
Chinese: A. PI是一种稳定币，所有PI的发行都是通过质押借贷产生，您可以通过质押借出一定的PI，也可以去交易市场购买PI
